OL,5, Grieving someone you love deeply is not
OL,6, easy to do in public, the Queen once   
OL,7, said, the former Archbishop of York Dr 
OL,8, John Sentamu has revealed.             
OL,10,FSpeaking to the BBC, Dr Sentamu        
OL,11,Frecalled the words in a "most wonderful
OL,12,Fletter" the Queen wrote to him after   
OL,13,FPrince Philip died last year.          
OL,15,FHe added his thoughts were with King   
OL,16,FCharles and the Royal Family who "are  
OL,17,Fgrieving publicly".                    
OL,19,FDr Sentamu also said the Queen did not 
OL,20,Fwant a "long, boring" funeral service. 
